&lt;p&gt;Welcome to another exciting year at LCS! &amp;nbsp;We have a number of events scheduled for the children and for families. &amp;nbsp;Please join us at the following upcoming events:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;Meet Your Teacher Open House&lt;/strong&gt; is scheduled for 2pm-3pm on Tuesday, September 4th.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On the first day of school, please join the PTO for a &lt;strong&gt;Welcome Back Coffee&lt;/strong&gt; at 9:15am on Thursday, September 6th. &amp;nbsp;We will be meeting just next door to LCS, upstairs at the Liberty Corner Presbyterian Church (LCPC). &amp;nbsp;Meet the PTO board members, hear more about upcoming events, sign up to help at PTO events, or just enjoy the camaraderie&amp;nbsp;of other parents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Back to School Night&lt;/strong&gt; will be on Thursday, September 13, 6-9:15pm. &amp;nbsp;Please try to attend to see the presentations the teachers have prepared to show you how your child&#39;s day runs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For anyone who would like to volunteer in the classroom, please attend one of the two &lt;strong&gt;Volunteer Orientation&lt;/strong&gt; sessions on October 3rd, at 9:30am or 7:00pm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lastly, please mark your calendars for the PTO&#39;s annual &lt;strong&gt;Pizza Night&lt;/strong&gt; on Friday, September 21st. &amp;nbsp;More details and forms will be available shortly.&lt;/p&gt;
